quran[69]{c,v,t}:
  29,1,"Alɩf, Laam, Miim."
  29,2,"Rẽ yĩngɑ nebã tẽedɑme tɩ b nɑ n bɑs-b-lɑ woto n kɑ zɑrb-b n ges lɑ?"
  29,3,"Lɑ sɩdɑ, Tõnd zɑrbɑ sẽn deng-b bãmb tɑoorã; lɑ tɩ Wẽnd na bãng neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩdã, A nɑ bãng zĩrimbe-nebã me."
  29,4,"Bɩ neb nins sẽn tʋmd tʋʋm-wẽnɑ tẽedɑme tɩ b nɑ n põsɑ Tõndo? B sẽn sãmbd yɩ wẽngɑ."
  29,5,"Ned ning sẽn tẽed Wẽnd segbã, bɩ ɑ bãng tɩ Wẽnd sɑsɑ wã wɑtɑme, lɑ Yẽnda la a Wʋmd la a Bãngda."
  29,6,"Lɑ ned ning sẽn nidg-ɑ pãngɑ, ɑ nidgdɑ pãng ɑ meng yĩngɑ; ad Wẽnd yɑɑ Sek-m-meng Soɑb n yi a bõn-nɑɑndsã fãɑ gilli."
  29,7,"Lɑ neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩdã lɑ b tʋm tʋʋm-sõamã wã, D nɑ lʋd b tʋʋm wẽnã, lɑ D nɑ rol-b rolb sõmblem sẽn yɩɩd bãmb sẽn dɑ tʋmdã."
  29,8,"Lɑ Tõnd sɑglɑ ninsɑɑl ne ɑ roɑgdb ɑ yiibã sɑglg sẽn be neere, lɑ b sã n pẽdg foo tɩ f lɑgem Mɑɑm ne bũmb fo sẽn kɑ tɑr ɑ bãngre, bɩ f rɑ tũ-b ye, Mɑm nengẽ lɑ yãmb lebgr zĩig tɩ M rol yãmb y sẽn dɑg n tʋmdã."
  29,9,"Lɑ D nɑ kẽes neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩd lɑ b tʋm tʋʋm-sõamã nin-sõmã wã pʋgẽ."
  29,10,"Lɑ bee nebã pʋgẽ ned sẽn yete: ""tõnd kõo sɩd ne Wẽnde"". Lɑ b sã n nams-ɑ Wẽnd dĩinɑ poorẽ lɑ ɑ sẽn dɩkd nebã mɑɑn-wẽnsã wɑlɑ Wẽnd noangã; lɑ tɩ sõngr sã n yi Wẽnd nengẽ n wɑ, a nɑ yeele: ""ad tõnd rɑ naɑgɑ yãmbɑ"". Rẽ yĩngɑ Wẽnd kɑ mi sẽn be bõn-nɑɑndsã sũy pʋsẽ?"
  29,11,"Lɑ tɩ Wẽnd nɑ bãng neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩdã, A na bãng munaafɩgsã me."
  29,12,"Lɑ kɩfr-rãmbã yeelɑ muumin-rãmbã: ""tũ-y tõnd sorã tɩ tõnd tʋk yãmb tʋʋm-tuutɩ wã rolbo"". Lɑ b yɑool n kɑ na n tʋk b tʋʋm-tuutɩ wã rolb baa fʋɩ ye, lɑ sɩdã b yɑɑ zĩrimbe-nebɑ."
  29,13,"Lɑ tɩ b na tʋk b tʋʋm-tuutɩ wã lɑ tʋʋm-tuutɩ n pɑɑs b tʋʋm-tuutɩ wã, lɑ tɩ b nɑ sok-b Yikrã rɑɑre b sẽn dɑ wãadgd n dogendẽ wã."
  29,14,"Lɑ sɩd la hakɩɩka tõnd tʋmɑ ɑ Nuuh ɑ nebã nengẽ, t'ɑ zĩnd b nengẽ yʋʋm pis-nu sẽn paoog yʋʋm tusri, tɩ koomã rɩ-bɑ, tɩ b yɑɑ wẽgdbɑ."
  29,15,"Tɩ tõnd tɩlg yẽndɑ lɑ koglgã rãmbɑ, lɑ D maan-a t'ɑ yaa tɑgs-n-gesg bõn-nɑɑndsã yĩngɑ."
  29,16,"Lɑ f tẽeg ɑ ɭbrɑɑhɩɩm yellã, ɑ sẽn wɑ n yeel ɑ nebã: ""tũ-y Wẽnd lɑ y zoe-A tɩ rẽnda n sõmb y yĩng tɩ yãmb sã n yɩ n miẽ."
  29,17,"Yãmb sẽn tũud zẽng sẽn kɑ Wẽndã yɑɑ rʋbs bɑlɑ, lɑ y wʋgd zĩri; ad yãmb sẽn bõosd-b rãmbã kɑ so rɩtl yãmb yĩng ye, bɩ y bao rɩtlã Wẽnd nengẽ lɑ y tũ-A lɑ y soees-A, Yẽndɑ nengẽ lɑ y na n lebe."
  29,18,"La tɩ b sã n yags foom, ad zãma sẽn reng bãmb taoor rag n yagsame, la ka rog ne Tẽn-tʋʋm rẽnda taasg sẽn vẽnege."
  29,19,"Rẽ yĩngɑ bãmb kɑ yã Wẽnd sẽn sɩngd naanegã to-to lɑ A leb n wɑ vʋʋg-ɑ wã lɑ? Ad wã yɑɑ yol-yol ne Wẽnde."
  29,20,"Yeele: ""kẽn-y tẽngã pʋgẽ n ges A sẽn sɩng naanegã to-to wã, rẽ poorẽ tɩ Wẽnd nɑ n yẽbg vʋʋgrã sẽn yɑɑ yaoolem naanegã; ad Wẽnd yɑɑ bũmb fãɑ Tõodɑ."
  29,21,"A nɑmesdɑ A sẽn dɑt-ɑ soɑbɑ, lɑ A yolsd A sẽn dɑt-ɑ soɑbɑ, lɑ yɑɑ Yẽ nengẽ lɑ b nɑ n lebs yãmbɑ."
  29,22,"Lɑ yãmb kɑ tar põsg zĩig tẽng zug bɩ sɑɑsẽ ye. Y le kɑ tɑr lɑlld lɑ sõngd zẽng sẽn kɑ Wẽnde."
  29,23,"Lɑ neb nins sẽn kɩfl ne Wẽnd goɑmã lɑ A segbã, bãmb rãmb n yãk b yɑm n yi Mɑm yolsgã, lɑ bãmb rãmbã, naon-zɑbdg n be b yĩngɑ."
  29,24,"T'ɑ nebã kɑ tɑll leokr sã n kɑ b sẽn yeele: ""kʋ-y-yã-a mɑɑ y yõog-ɑ bugum"" .Tɩ Wẽnd põsg-ɑ n yi bugmã; ad wãnde pʋgẽ wã tags-n-gesg-rãmb n be ne neb nins sẽn kõt-b sɩdã."
  29,25,"Lɑ ɑ le yeele: ""ɑd bũmb ningã yãmb sẽn dɩk zẽng sẽn kɑ Wẽndã yãmb ne tɑɑb sʋk noanglem yĩng dũni vɩɩmã pʋgẽ wã, yɑɑ rʋbs bɑlɑ. Rẽ poorẽ yãmb nɑ n kɩfla tɑɑb Yikrã rɑɑre, lɑ yãmb sãndɑ nɑ n kãɑbdɑ sãndɑ, lɑ yãmb kõom zĩig nɑ n yɩɩ bugmã, lɑ y kɑ nɑ n tɑll sõngdb me ye. Lɑ sõngdb kɑ nɑ n zĩnd y yĩng me ye."
  29,26,"T'ɑ Lʋʋṭ kõ-a sɩd lɑ ɑ yeele: ""ɑd mɑm na n maana higra n tʋg m Soɑbã nengẽ, ad Yẽnda, Yẽ lɑ zɩsgr Naab lɑ bʋʋd Mitɑ''."
  29,27,"Lɑ Tõnd kõ-a ɑ ɭsḥɑɑk lɑ ɑ Yɑɑkʋʋbɑ, lɑ d ning Nabiyaamdem lɑ Sebrã ɑ koɑmbã pʋgẽ, lɑ d kõ-a ɑ keoorã dũni. La ad yaoolem daarã ɑ nɑ n nɑɑgɑ nin-sõmã wã."
  29,28,"Lɑ f tẽeg Tõnd sẽn tʋm ɑ Lʋʋṭ, ɑ sẽn wɑ n yeel ɑ nebã: ""ad yãmb tʋmdɑ yel-wẽn ned ba ɑ yembr sẽn kɑ reng yãmb n tʋm ɑ bʋud bõn-naandsã pʋgẽ''."
  29,29,"Yãmb maanda kẽed-n-taar ne rapã lɑ y bɑsd pɑgbã, lɑ y gɩt soay lɑ y kɩɩsd Wẽnd yãmb bool-tɑɑbã zĩigẽ? T'ɑ nebã kɑ tɑll leokr sã n kɑ b sẽn yeele: ''bɩ f wɑ ne Wẽnd noangã tɩ f sã n yɑɑ sɩd-soɑbɑ""."
  29,30,"T'a yeele: ""Wẽnde! sõng-m tɩ m tõog sãamdbã zãma""."
  29,31,"Lɑ Tõnd Tẽn-tʋmdbã sẽn wɑ n wɑ ɑ ɭbrɑɑhɩɩm nengẽ ne sũ-noogrã, b yeelame: ""ad tõnd nɑ n halka tẽn-kãngã rãmbã, ad a nebã rɑ yɩɩ wẽgdbɑ""."
  29,32,"A (ɭbraahɩɩm) yeel-b lame: ""ad ɑ Lʋʋṭ bee beenẽ"", tɩ b yeele: ""tõnd n yɩɩd minim ne neb sẽn be tẽngã pʋgẽ, tõnd nɑ n põsgɑ yẽnda la ɑ zɑkã rãmbɑ, rẽndɑ ɑ pɑgã bɑlɑ, ɑ nɑɑgɑ b sẽn na n halkã rãmbã''."
  29,33,"Lɑ Tõnd tẽn-tʋmdbã sẽn wɑ n tɑ ɑ Lʋʋṭ nengẽ wã, a sũurã sãama b yĩnga, a sẽn ka tar pãng n na n sõng-bã, lɑ b yeelyã: ""rɑ yεεs ye, rɑ sãam f sũur ye, ad d nɑ n põsgɑ foom ne f zɑkã rãmbɑ, rẽndɑ fo pɑgã bɑlɑ, ɑ nɑɑgɑ b sẽn na n halkã rãmba."
  29,34,"Ad tõnd nɑ n sikɑ noang tɩ yi sɑɑgẽ wã tẽn-kãngã rãmbã zugu, b sẽn dɑ yɩ n tɑrd n bɑsd dĩinã yĩngɑ."
  29,35,"Lɑ sɩd la hɑkɩɩkɑ Tõnd basa a pʋgẽ, yel-soalem-vẽenes sẽn tɑgsdbã yĩngɑ."
  29,36,"Lɑ D tʋm Mɑdyɑn, b saam-biiga a Sʋ'ʿayba b nengẽ, t'ɑ yeele: ""Yaa yãmb m nebɑ! Tũ-y Wẽnd lɑ y tẽ Yɑoolem dɑɑrã, lɑ y rɑ yɩ sãɑmdb n gɩlgd tẽngã pʋgẽ ye."
  29,37,"Tɩ b yags-a, tɩ miim-kεgengã rɩk-b tɩ b lebg kɩɩms n wũg b zɑgsã pʋsẽ."
  29,38,"Lɑ tẽeg-y aʿAad lɑ a Ṯamuud rãmb yelle; sɩd la hakɩɩka, b zagsã yɩɩ vẽeneg ne yãmba, lɑ ɑ sʋɩtãan fɑɑsɑ b tʋʋmã n kõ-bɑ, n gɩd-b n yiis sorẽ wã, lɑ b yɑool n yɩɩ nenem-vẽenes rãmbɑ ne yεlɑ fãɑ."
  29,39,"Lɑ y tẽeg ɑ Kaarʋʋn lɑ ɑ Fɩr'ʿaoon lɑ ɑ Haɑmɑɑn rãmb yelle; lɑ sɩd la hakɩɩka ɑ Musɑ wɑa b nengẽ ne yel-vẽenesã tɩ b mɑɑn wɑoog-m-meng tẽngã pʋgẽ, lɑ b kɑ yɩ põsdb ye."
  29,40,"La ned kam fãa Tõnd yõk-ɑ-lɑ ne ɑ zunuubu. Zĩndɑ b pʋgẽ Tõnd sẽn tʋm sobg t'ɑ halk-ba, zĩndɑ b pʋgẽ tãsg sẽn pɑɑme, zĩnda b pʋgẽ Tõnd sẽn kɩt tɩ tẽngã vel-bɑ, zĩnda b pʋgẽ Tõnd sẽn bõre. Wẽnd kɑ yɩ n nɑ n wẽg-b ye, lɑ yɑɑ bãmb n dɑ yɩ n wẽgd b mense."
  29,41,"Neb nins sẽn dɩk zẽng sẽn kɑ Wẽnd n mɑɑn b lɑll-n-tɑɑsã bilgr yɑɑ wɑlɑ sʋlg sẽn wʋg ɑ roogo, lɑ ad zɑk sẽn yɩɩd vɑleng yɑɑ sʋlg zɑkɑ, tɩ b sã n da miime."
  29,42,"Ad Wẽnd mii bũmb ningã b sẽn boond zẽms sẽn kɑ Yẽnda wã, lɑ Yẽ lɑ ɑ Wilb Naabɑ n ya ɑ Bʋʋd Minim Naaba."
  29,43,"Lɑ yɑɑ bilg-bãmbã lɑ Tõnd rɩkd n wĩngd nebã, lɑ kɑ wʋmd ɑ võorã rẽndɑ yam-bεεl rãmbã."
  29,44,"Wẽnd nɑɑnɑ sɑɑsã lɑ tẽngã sɩd yĩngɑ, ad wãnde pʋgẽ wã yel-soalem bee beenẽ sɩd-kõtbã yĩngɑ."
  29,45,"Kɑrem b sẽn tʋm tɩ wɑ fo nengẽ tɩ be Gafẽ wã, lɑ f yɑls Pʋʋsgã, ad Pʋʋsgã gũudɑme n yit yel-wẽn lɑ yel-kiti tʋʋmɑ, lɑ ad Wẽnd yʋʋrã tẽegrã n yɩɩd bedrem, lɑ Wẽnd mii yãmb sẽn mɑɑndã."
  29,46,"Lɑ y rɑ wẽ no-koεεmd ne Gafã rãmb rẽndɑ ne sẽn sõmbe, rẽndɑ b nins sẽn wẽgbã; lɑ y yele: ""tõnd kõo sɩd ne b sẽn sik tɩ wɑ tõnd nengẽ lɑ yãmb nengẽ wã; lɑ tõnd Soɑbã ne yãmb Soɑbã yɑa A Yembre, lɑ tõnd yɑɑ sak-n-tũ rãmb A yĩngɑ''."
  29,47,"Lɑ yɑɑ woto bɑla lɑ Tõnd sik Gafã tɩ wɑ fo nengẽ; rẽnd neb nins Tõnd sẽn kɩs Gafã kõtɑ sɩd ne-a (Alkʋrãanã), lɑ bee bãmbã (Mɑk kɩfr-dãmbã) pʋgẽ sẽn kõt sɩd ne-a. Lɑ kɑ yɑgsd Tõnd goɑmã ne pʋ-toog rẽndɑ kɩfr-dãmbã."
  29,48,"Lɑ fo rɑ kɑ yɩ tɑoor tɩ Alkʋrãɑnɑ nɑ n pɑ wɑ n da kɑremd Gaf ye, fo kɑ yɩ n gʋlsdẽ me ye; sã n da yɩ woto, neb nins sẽn kɩɩsdb sɩdã rag n na n maana sik a zugu."
  29,49,"Ka woto ye, ad a yaa Goam sẽn be bãngdbã yãadẽ, lɑ kɑ yɑgsd Tõnd Goɑmã ne pʋ-toog ralla wẽgdbã."
  29,50,"Lɑ b yeele: ""b kɑ nɑ n dɑg n sikẽ yel-soɑlem-dãmb sẽn yi ɑ Soɑbã nengẽ ɑ zugu?"" Yeele: ""ɑd yel-soɑlem-dãmbã fãɑ yɑɑ Wẽnd nengẽ bɑl lɑ be, lɑ mɑm kɑ yɩ rallɑ bugsd sẽn yɑɑ vẽenegɑ''."
  29,51,"Lɑ rẽ yĩngɑ Tõnd sẽn sik Gafã tɩ b kɑremd-ɑ bãmb zugã kɑ sek bãmbɑ? Ad rẽndɑ pʋgẽ wã yɑɑ yolsg lɑ tẽegr n be beenẽ neb nins sẽn kõt-b sɩdã yĩngɑ."
  29,52,"Yeele: ''mɑɑm ne yãmb sʋkɑ, Wẽnd seedgã sekame; A mii sẽn be sɑɑsẽ lɑ tẽngẽ, lɑ neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩd ne zĩri wã lɑ b kɩfl ne Wẽndã, bãmb-rãmb lɑ bõndbã."
  29,53,"Lɑ b yãgdɑme tɩ fo wɑ ne naongã, lɑ sã n kɑ sɑsɑ sẽn yãk n kõ yĩngɑ, noangã rag n nɑ pɑɑm-bɑ, lɑ tɩ naongã nɑ pɑɑm-b ne lingr tɩ b kɑ bãng ye."
  29,54,"B yãgdɑme tɩ fo wɑ ne naongã, lɑ ad Gεhɑnnɑm nɑ n gũbgɑ kɩfr-dãmbã."
  29,55,"Rɑar ning naongã sẽn nɑ n yit b yĩngrã lɑ b naoã tẽngrã wεεngẽ n sudgd-ba [lɑ b yet-ba]: "" lemb-y y sẽn dɑ yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã""."
  29,56,"Yaa yãmb M yembs nins sẽn kõ sɩdɑ! Ad Mɑm tẽngã yɑlmɑme, bɩ y tũ mɑɑm bɑlɑ."
  29,57,"Yõor fãɑ nɑ n lembɑ kũum, rẽ poorẽ yɑɑ Tõnd nengẽ lɑ b nɑ n lebs yãmbɑ."
  29,58,"Lɑ neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd lɑ b tʋm tʋʋm-sõmã wã, Tõnd nɑ sik-b arzãn rotẽ tɩ ko-sood zoet b tẽngre, tɩ b yɑɑ pɑɑdb ɑ pʋgẽ; ɑd tʋmdbã keoor yɩ neere."
  29,59,"La neb nins sẽn maan sugrã la b rɩk b mensã n rell b Soabã, b keoor be neere."
  29,60,"Lɑ sõor wɑoog bõn-yãnemdɩ sẽn kɑ tõe n tʋkd mɑ b bɑo b rɩtlã, ɑd yɑɑ Wẽnd n dɩlgd bãmb lɑ yãmbɑ, lɑ Yẽndɑ lɑ Wʋmdã lɑ Mittã."
  29,61,"Lɑ tɩ fo sã n sok-b tɩ ãnd n nɑɑn sɑɑsã lɑ tẽngã lɑ ɑ nom wĩntoogã lɑ kiuugã? B nɑ yeel tɩ yɑɑ Wẽnde. La mɑɑnɑ ɑ wãn tɩ b gõdgd n basd so-tɩrgã?"
  29,62,"Wẽnd yɑlgdɑ rɩtlã n kõt A sẽn dɑt-b rãmb A yembsã pʋgẽ lɑ A weoogd A sẽn dɑt-b rãmbɑ; ad Wẽnd yɑɑ Mit ne bũmb fãɑ."
  29,63,"Lɑ tɩ fo sã n sok-b tɩ ãnd n sikd koomã tɩ yit sɑɑgẽ wã n tɑll-ɑ n vʋʋg tẽngã ɑ sẽn ki loogr poore? B nɑ yeel tɩ yɑɑ Wẽnde. Yeele: ""Wẽnd n so pẽgre"". Ad b wʋsgã fãɑ ka tagsd ye."
  29,64,"Lɑ dũni-kãngã kɑ baa fʋɩ n zʋʋg kɩdeng la reem ye, lɑ ad Yɑoolem zɑkã, yẽ lɑ vɩɩm sẽn kɑ sɑɑbã tɩ b sã n dɑ yɩɩme n miẽ."
  29,65,"La b sã n wa zomb koom koglgo lɑ b sẽn n bõosd Wẽnde tɩ b yɑɑ sẽn n yɩlg b pʋs A kosgẽ wã; lɑ A sã n tɩlg-b n yiis yɩngã lɑ b sẽn mɑɑnd lɑgem-n-tɑɑr ne-A."
  29,66,"Bʋl yĩng tɩ b na kɩfl ne A sẽn n kõ bãmbã; b mɑɑn wʋm-noog tɩ bɩlf bɑlɑ b nɑ bãnge."
  29,67,"Rẽ yĩngɑ bãmb ka yãnd tɩ Tõnd kõo bãmb Lohorem zĩig sẽn yaa bas-m-yam, tɩ b yaool n tabsda nebã bãmb tẽn-kɩrensã. Rẽ yĩngɑ bãmb kɩta sɩd ne zɑɑlem la b kɩfend ne Wẽnd neemã wã?"
  29,68,"Lɑ ãnd n yɩɩd wẽgb ne ned ning sẽn wãagd-ɑ zĩri n dogl Wẽnd tɩ kɑ yɩ ne sɩda maa a yagsd sɩdã a sẽn wa n wa-a wã? Rẽ yĩnga, ka Gεhannem la kɩfr-rãmb gãag zĩigã?"
  29,69,"Lɑ neb nins sẽn nidg-b pãng Tõnd yĩngã, D nɑ kãndg-b D soyã zugu, lɑ bãng tɩ Wẽnd bee ne neb nins sẽn yɑɑ mɑnegdbã."
